title: Any Obak color variations/printing mishaps out there?
author: shammus

posts.post_title: Any Obak color variations/printing mishaps out there?
posts.post_content:
Just seeing if anyone has any Obak printing goofs they wouldn't mind parting with.  Looking for severe miscuts, doubleprinted backs, ghosts, t212-2 "bluegrass" variations, etc..etc..  Will pay strong prices for severe examples.  Thanks in advance....

Brian

They are tough Brian......Except for a proof and another strip of 4 I haven't seen a lot of them. Here is an Egan '09 I picked up not too long ago (bottom right) with a double strike back.
..Just be glad they aren't T206's, because then if you found one it would be tons of money. Good luck in the quest...
Thanks Leon.  The Eagan is a nice card.  I bought a double printed back just like that from Mark Macrae a while back.  I think the player was Hitt if I recall....
